  <brief_title>Effects of Hypoglycemic Drugs on Testosterone Levels in Type 2 Diabetes Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Continuous Subcutaneous Insulin Infusion and Oral Hypoglycemic Drugs on Testosterone Levels in Type 2 Diabetes Patients</official_title>
