  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will assess the total testosterone and sex hormone-binding globulin levels in men
      with type 2 diabetes before and after continuous subcutaneous insulin infusion and
      hypoglycemic drugs treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
